    "url": "/upcoming",
    "title": "Upcoming articles",
    "body": " Articles under process. Articles based on the following list of papers have been received by CosmicVarta and are under the process of editing by our team memebers. Usually the articles stay with our editors for a period of xx to yy days, after which you may expect the article to be published on the main webpage. 1. Complex optical/UV and X-ray variability in Seyfert 1 galaxy Mrk 509 2. Kiloparsec-scale AGN Outflows and Feedback in Merger-Free Galaxies 3. Extreme Variability and Episodic Lifetime of Quasars 4. Polar dust obscuration in broad-line active galaxies from the XMM-XXL field 5. A phenomenological model for measuring generalised Faraday rotation 6. SDSS J154751. 94+025550 with double-peaked broad Hβbut single-peaked broad Hα: a candidate for central binary black hole system? 7. Cosmological impact of redshift drift measurements Please enable JavaScript to view the comments powered by Disqus. "
